'''Idmim''' neɣ '''Admam''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: '''Crataegus''') d [[tawsit (tudersent)|tawsit]] n [[Aseklu|yisekla]] d [[tamdikt|tmedkin]] timsennenin i d-ittemɣayen deg wezgen agafan n tegnit. Tawsit-a d tin yeṭṭafaren [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[Tanejjikt|tnejjikin]]. 

Amdan n [[Talmest|telmas]] n tewsit-a d win yemgaraden seg usesmel ɣer wayeṭ, maca imusnawen mtawan ɣef wazal n 200 n telmas. Tilmas yettusxedmen yakk s waṭas i lmend n iylan-is isnajjyanen d [[idmim azeggaɣ]] (''Crataegus monogyna'') yakk d [[idmim busennan|yidmim busennan]] (''Crataegus laevigata''), ma d [[tubrazt]] (''Crataegus azarolus'') d tin i d-issemɣayen igumma yettwaččayen.  

== Asesmel ==
Tawsit-a tettwaglem deg useggas n [[1753]] sɣur umusnaw n ugama [[Carl Von Linné]]. 

Aguccel n telmas yeṭṭafaren tawsit n yidmim d ayen imrayen (iweɛṛen) s usrag n wefrar (af ssebba n ssehala) n [[asregnet|usregnet]] gar n telmas yemgaraden n yidmim s ufaras [[irzi|yirza]].
